short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Predicts the colleges you can get into based on your JEE Main score.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The JEE Main College Predictor Chrome Extension is a powerful tool designed to help students predict the colleges they can secure admission to based on their JEE Main scores. This user-friendly extension offers a quick and convenient way to explore potential colleges, ensuring that students make informed decisions about their future education.

Features:

1. Easy to Use: Simply enter your JEE Main score, select your category and gender, and get instant predictions.
2. Comprehensive Data: Access a wide range of colleges and programs, with detailed opening and closing ranks for different categories.
3. Personalized Results: Tailor your search based on your specific criteria to find the best possible college options.
4. Offline Access: Enjoy the convenience of using the predictor without the need for an internet connection.
5. Free to Use: All features are available for free, making it accessible to all students.
Prepare for your future with confidence using the JEE Main College Predictor Chrome Extension!
